{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tipping-content-js","path":"/viet_nam","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Tipping is not expected in Vietnam with the exception of bellhops in high-end hotels, and the Vietnamese themselves don't do it, though tips will not be refused if offered. Some establishments which are used to serving Western tourists have come to expect tips, though it is still perfectly acceptable not to tip. In any case, the price quoted to you is often many times what locals will pay, so tipping can be considered unnecessary in most circumstances. To avoid paying an involuntary tip when a taxi driver claims he doesn't have small change always try to carry small denominations.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/viet_nam","title":"Viet Nam","author":"Joni","date":"2019-11-22","image":"viet_nam.jpg"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5,"src":"/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/90537/viet_nam.jpg","srcSet":"/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/b3ebb/viet_nam.jpg 270w,\n/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/95b54/viet_nam.jpg 540w,\n/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/90537/viet_nam.jpg 1080w,\n/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/3cda3/viet_nam.jpg 1620w,\n/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/1f682/viet_nam.jpg 2160w,\n/static/584c97f239c345c38bb013a431e75cbf/0b354/viet_nam.jpg 6000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"image":"viet_nam.jpg"}}}